{"Name":"Gourmet Xchange","ShortName":"Gourmet Xchange","Description":"Gourmet Xchange by CapitaLand Development (CLD) is set to redefine Singapore’s food manufacturing landscape with a state-of-the-art nine-storey food factory at Kallang Way. Spanning 44,107 sqm, the development will house 284 industrial, F\u0026B, and retail units with efficient 40-footer ramp-up access and large, flexible floor plates, catering to both artisanal producers and large-scale operators. ","StartUrl":"/","Display":"standalone","BackgroundColor":"#ffffff","ThemeColor":"#041e42","Orientation":"portrait","Icons":[{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/5c9f0347-a8d1-40f1-ae03-32f8630b143b","Sizes":"192x192","Type":"image/png"},{"Src":"https://rtdbookappointment.s3.ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/Bookappointment/Property/5c9f0347-a8d1-40f1-ae03-32f8630b143b","Sizes":"512x512","Type":"image/png"}]}